summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsVeganGive BackMaybelline New York's Ultra Slim Brow Pencil delivers precisely defined brows for a natural brow look. Featuring a 1.5 mm precision tip and spoolie brush.
details: DetailsBenefitsUltra slim defining brow pencil features a one & a half millimeter tip and spoolie brush for a natural brow lookNo pencil breakage & no color streaksUltra-smooth formulaItem 2545919How To UseDraw small, light strokes along the brow contour. Use the brush to groom hairs upward and outward to blend color and set brows.Eye cosmetics in a scratched, infected, or irritated eye and scratches from cosmetics eye applicators can lead to eye damage and in extreme cases, even blindness. If your eye is scratched stop using all eye cosmetics and go to an ophthalmologist immediately. Never apply this product in a moving vehicle. Do not use near fire, flame, or heat.IngredientsHydrogenated Soybean Oil, Synthetic Japan Wax, Stearic Acid, Synthetic Fluorphlogopite, Hydrogenated Coco-Glycerides, Zinc Stearate, Polyglyceryl-2 Triisostearate, Myristyl Myristate, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Tocopherol. May Contain: CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499/Iron Oxides, CI 77891/Titanium Dioxide.
how_to_use: Draw small, light strokes along the brow contour. Use the brush to groom hairs upward and outward to blend color and set brows.Eye cosmetics in a scratched, infected, or irritated eye and scratches from cosmetics eye applicators can lead to eye damage and in extreme cases, even blindness. If your eye is scratched stop using all eye cosmetics and go to an ophthalmologist immediately. Never apply this product in a moving vehicle. Do not use near fire, flame, or heat.

reviews.headline: I recommend this product.
reviews.comments: I like this product very much and it's not waterproof which is good

reviews.headline: Feather like lashes
reviews.comments: I really like the applicator wand for the mascara. I used to think that mascara always clumped up the lashes and wonder how people abroad did it. But this clumps my lashes the least out of the other mascaras i've tried

reviews.headline: Natural look
reviews.comments: This is a good budget friendly eyebrow pencil that comes with a brush, which is very helpful for shaping the brows and even guiding when trimming. The pencil is easy to use and the brush softens the look for a more natural finish. The color is balanced, not too dark or too light, and it blends in to blur seamlessly with the natural brow. It does not last the whole day, but it stays in place for a couple of hours.

reviews.headline: The Brow  with a fine line
reviews.comments: This I always get..

reviews.headline: Very good!
reviews.comments: It's a great mascara and very volumizing. I like to pair it with a lash serum and it makes it look like I have fake lashes on. I also love how easy it is to remove. Definitely would recommend!

reviews.headline: Love it!!
reviews.comments: This product is so good!!! It makes my eye browse look so natural!

reviews.headline: My go to brow pencil!
reviews.comments: I have used this brow pencil for years and love it. It compares to namebrands for a fraction of the cost. I used others and always return to this brow pencil.

reviews.headline: Smudgy yet hard to remove
reviews.comments: It looks pretty for about an hour. After that it smudges around my eyes and is also hard to remove at the end of the day.

reviews.headline: Smooth
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Maybelline Express Brow Shaping Pencil is quick, easy, and perfect for natural-looking brows. The pencil glides on smoothly, fills gaps effortlessly, and the built-in spoolie blends well. Great for daily use and beginners!

reviews.headline: Easy to use and natural looking
reviews.comments: I was looking for a drugstore dupe to replace my Bennefit brow pencil and came across this. It's easy to use and looks natural because of how small the pencil is. It also stays all day. Overall, very happy with the product and will buy again.

reviews.headline: It Does The Length Thing
reviews.comments: A lovely mascara that does what the title says. Its really great if youre looking for something natural to wear on the daily.

reviews.headline: The best mascara ever!
reviews.comments: This is my favorite mascara to use everyday and also for events!! This is the best formula that works with my lashes! Gone through 2 already and will repurchase for the rest of my life.

reviews.headline: I would buy this product over most others
reviews.comments: I enjoyed the end result, although it took many coats to cover my lashes. I also found it a little frustrating that I couldn't apply a coat after it dries but I am overall fine with that. I was pleased with the amount for the cost of this product.

reviews.headline: NOT A FAN
reviews.comments: CHALKY, DOESN'T GLIDE ON AND POWDER DOES NOT STICK

reviews.headline: good
reviews.comments: it holds my lashes up and lastes

reviews.headline: I love definitely think i'm going to continue to buy. Afford
reviews.comments: Thin pencil tip & comes with a spoolie. Thin tip allows you to replicate realistic brow hairs. As someone who has to draw on a part of their eyebrow I love it.

reviews.headline: I buy this all the time.
reviews.comments: I like this pencil to touch up my eye brows. It is just the right color.

reviews.headline: A staple
reviews.comments: Ive been using this past 2 years and I love it.  I have thick, straight lashes. & the Waterproof one holds my curl better, and I hope they never discontinue!. Cant beat it for the price,- Never had issues with Flaking.

reviews.headline: Best value
reviews.comments: I've tried so many mascaras- expensive, viral, etc. This is one I keep coming back to. Lengthens, thickens without messy clumping, and the waterproof version never smudges no matter what.

reviews.headline: Made My Lashes Fall Out ‚Äì Avoid!
reviews.comments: I used this serum as directed and instead of volume/ length, my lashes started falling out. They became thin and patchy within days. I stopped using it immediately & I returned it. Totally disappointed, definitely not worth the risk.

faceoff_positive.comments: I have very light, straight invisible lashes.  This is a side-by-side of my eyes with and without this mascara.  Not all mascaras can tackle lower lashes, but just look!  My one complaint is that for the first half hour of wear, I find smudges right below my eyebrows.  But I love the result too much to care!  I've been a Lash Sensational addict for years, but this gets my lower lashes looking amazing.  I have a new HG!
faceoff_positive.headline: Results speak for themselves

faceoff_negative.comments: I bought this Tuesday I was looking for a waterproof mascara and I wish that I had went with a different one cause this did clump my lashes together and it looked horrible! It's not going to stop me from trying another waterproof one, but any suggestions? Ive used Maybelline products since I was a teenager, just need to find the right waterproof mascara for me!
faceoff_negative.headline: Looking for the right one for me
